== 反響 ==

=== 評價 ===

電影收穫了影評人的好評，克隆尼、坎卓克與法蜜嘉的表現獲得廣泛的讚譽<ref name="HR 2009-09-07">{{cite web|last=Fernandez|first=Jay A.|title=Optimism in 'Air' as Telluride ends|work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=September 7, 2009|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i27b2ea26515fca07b9a6161e18d88d29|accessdate=September 7, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090911080352/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i27b2ea26515fca07b9a6161e18d88d29|archivedate=2009-09-11}}</ref>。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的269篇專業影評文章，其中244篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為91%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]8.1分（滿分10分）<ref name="rot">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/up_in_the_air_2009/|title=Up in the Air (2009)|publisher=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=June 11, 2010|archive-date=2010-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100623023657/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/up_in_the_air_2009/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的36篇評論文章，其中32篇予以好評，無差評，4篇褒貶不一，平均分為83（滿分100）<ref name="meta">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/up-in-the-air|title=Up in the Air: Reviews (2009)|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=January 24, 2010|archive-date=2012-06-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68TzTCMV0?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/up-in-the-air|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 榮譽 ===

{{Main|在云端获奖与提名列表}}

《型男飛行日誌》榮獲各種獎項與提名，類別從認可電影本身、劇本、導演及剪輯，到3位主演——[[喬治·克隆尼|喬治·克隆尼]]、[[薇拉·法蜜嘉|薇拉·法蜜嘉]]和[[安娜·坎卓克|安娜·坎卓克]]的表現。電影入圍6項[[第82屆奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]的獎項，法蜜嘉及坎卓克也雙雙獲得最佳女配角的提名，然而電影最終未獲得任何獎項<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a206942/in-full-oscars-2010-the-winners.html|title=In Full: Oscars 2010 – The Winners|work=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|publisher={{link-en|阿榭特·菲利帕奇媒體|Hachette Filipacchi Médias|Hachette Filipacchi (UK) Ltd}}|first=Simon|last=Reynolds|date=March 7, 2010|accessdate=July 17, 2010|archive-date=2010-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100620151948/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a206942/in-full-oscars-2010-the-winners.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/82/nominees.html|title=Nominees & Winners for the 82nd Academy Awards|publisher=[[美國電影藝術與科學學會|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]]|accessdate=July 17, 2010|archive-date=2014-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001195317/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/82/nominees.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在{{link-en|第63屆英國電影學院獎|63rd British Academy Film Awards}}上，電影奪下5項提名，並從中抱回由瑞特曼與特納榮獲的最佳改編劇本獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/film-awards-nominations,949,BA.html|title=BAFTA Winners 2010|work=[[英國電影學院獎|British Academy Film Awards]]|date=January 21, 2010|publisher=[[英國電影和電視藝術學院|British Academy of Film and Television Arts]]|accessdate=July 17, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110917150110/http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/film-awards-nominations%2C949%2CBA.html|archivedate=2011年9月17日}}</ref>。《型男飛行日誌》於[[第67屆金球獎|第67屆金球獎]]上獲得5項提名，瑞特曼和特納榮獲最佳劇本獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://screencrave.com/2010-01-17/golden-globes-2010-winner-for-best-supporting-actor/|title=Golden Globes 2010: Christoph Waltz Wins for Best Supporting Actor|last=Ciarrocchi|first=Justine|date=January 17, 2010|work=Screen Crave|publisher=uCrave|accessdate=April 30, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726072539/http://screencrave.com/2010-01-17/golden-globes-2010-winner-for-best-supporting-actor/|archivedate=2011-07-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2009/dec/15/golden-globes-nominations|title=Golden Globes nominations: the 2010 list in full|date=December 15, 2009|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|publisher=[[衛報媒體集團|Guardian News and Media Limited]]|accessdate=January 31, 2010|location=London|archive-date=2014-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421220224/https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2009/dec/15/golden-globes-nominations|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

